                     <interp inst="t17530718-51-person461" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the prisoner upwards of a twelve-month, I do believe, indeed, my lord, he is a very honest man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17530718-51-person462">
                  John 
                  Pool 
               <interp inst="t17530718-51-person462" type="surname" value="Pool"></interp>
