            . I and the prisoner have been fellow servants together. I have known him above five years, we are <rs id="t17530718-51-deflabel267" type="occupation">hackney-coachmen</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17530718-51-defend454 t17530718-51-deflabel267"></join>, the prisoner always bore the character of a very honest man.</p>
